    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Brickadia》（又名：砖托邦）是一款极其自由的次世代沙盒游戏。每个创意工具（建筑、脚本等）都可以在多人游戏中即时使用。无需离开游戏，即可与好友一起打造庞大的世界、精巧的机械和全新的游戏模式。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>造出你心目中的构想。</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199420/extras/844432dfb2fb53c4b2e21f57cd098d8f.poster.avif?t=1765565621\" width=618 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199420/extras/844432dfb2fb53c4b2e21f57cd098d8f.webm?t=1765565621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >放下砖块造东西无比简单——只需使用我们直观强大的工具，你就能建造出高耸入云的大楼、新奇有趣的载具、不可思议的机械、细致入微的群岛、宇宙飞船、浩瀚城市。一切只看你的构想！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>让你的创作灵动鲜活。</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199420/extras/5e688447b48b1633fb334b310efc78d9.poster.avif?t=1765565621\" width=618 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199420/extras/5e688447b48b1633fb334b310efc78d9.webm?t=1765565621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Brickadia》具有惊人的动态物理系统，为你的创作灌输无限活力！凭靠线路逻辑，创造出配备按钮、开关、门、马达、电机、座椅、灯等各种交互的构建。设置带有逻辑门的简单电路，创造复杂的谜题和可怕的陷阱。一切操作都无需编写代码。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>个人形象，随你所想。</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199420/extras/f2dff7776c74595f5cc49ea0c74d2bff.poster.avif?t=1765565621\" width=618 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199420/extras/f2dff7776c74595f5cc49ea0c74d2bff.webm?t=1765565621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们广受爱戴的个人形象定制系统充满无限可能——使用数百个不同的部件，组装你自己独特的形象吧！更换任意身体部位、全身上下挂满配饰、戴上帽子、换上新发型、穿上漂亮的衣服，甚至加条尾巴？随意创造个人形象，想造多少造多少，喜欢的时候就换上！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>和其他玩家激烈对战。</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199420/extras/b1bd5a3ea406375cda2426749560f183.poster.avif?t=1765565621\" width=618 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199420/extras/b1bd5a3ea406375cda2426749560f183.webm?t=1765565621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >凭借我们灵活的游戏规则系统和海量的武器，任何建筑都可以摇身一变，成为激烈的战场！在你的建筑周围放置物品生成点和弹药拾取点，使用自定义游戏模式主持对外开放的服务器。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>尽情探索创作的海洋。</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199420/extras/ce2b08a236640f93a9ec13ffb33b7a53.poster.avif?t=1765565621\" width=618 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199420/extras/ce2b08a236640f93a9ec13ffb33b7a53.webm?t=1765565621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只想坐下来安心游玩？没问题。在《Brickadia》的世界里，直接感受其他玩家的创作从未变得如此简单。独自一人，或与好友共同探索我们游戏内丰富的创作艺廊。或许还能对作品进行重新组合，打造你自己的专属风格！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >实现真正的无限可能！</p>",
